qTotal.desc: Number of values in the field.

qIsNum.desc:
Optional parameter. This parameter is displayed if its value is true.
Is set to true if the field is a numeric.

qField.desc: Name of the field that is selected.

qLocked.desc:
Optional parameter. This parameter is displayed if its value is true.
Is set to true if the field is locked.

qOneAndOnlyOne.desc:
Optional parameter. This parameter is displayed if its value is true.
Property that is set to a field. Is set to true if the field cannot be unselected.

qTextSearch.desc:
Optional parameter.
Text that was used for the search. This parameter is filled when searching for a value and selecting it.

qSelectedCount.desc: Number of values that are selected.

qRangeInfo.desc:
Information about the range of selected values.
Is empty if there is no range of selected values.

qSortIndex.desc: Sort index of the field. Indexing starts from 0.

qStateCounts.desc: Number of values in a particular state.

qSelectedFieldSelectionInfo.desc: Information about the fields that are selected.

qNotSelectedFieldSelectionInfo.desc: Information about the fields that are not selected.

qSelectionThreshold.desc:
Maximum values to show in the current selections.
The default value is 6.
